3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - Kernel density estimation is also a common technique in machine learning for density estimation and anomaly detection. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses an algorithm for estimating the topology of the kernel distance using weighted Vietoris-Rips complexes, which is a topic in data structures and algorithms.
